*****************************
Statistics HATS@LPC Exercises
*****************************

External links:
 * `Indico Agenda of Statistics HATS@LPC 2014 <https://indico.cern.ch/event/315002/>`_.
 * documentation of theta and theta-auto http://theta-framework.org/


The exercises should be done in the following order:
 * Day 1 (Hypothesis Tests): After the :ref:`setup`, go on to :ref:`ex1`
 * Day 2 (Intervals and Limits): :ref:`ex2` and :ref:`ex3`
 * Day 3 (Advanced Models): :ref:`ex4` and `Tprime tutorial <https://twiki.cern.ch/twiki/bin/viewauth/CMS/TprimeTheta>`_

If you completed all exercises of the given day before the time is up, feel free to look at :ref:`extras` for more.

Related exercises using the RooStats-based "combine" tool can be found on the `CMSDAS Statistics page <https://twiki.cern.ch/twiki/bin/view/CMS/SWGuideCMSDataAnalysisSchoolStatistics2014>`_.


